Expanding the Divine Feminine

25-Apr-2016

While the merging of the Divine Feminine and the Divine Masculine is important for Balance, right now the Divine Feminine requires attention, support and nurturing. Remember that the Divine Feminine is Source and has essences of receiving, being, allowing, flowing and other yin qualities. As we honor our Divine Feminine, we help to raise our own consciousness and global consciousness, for the vibration and Power of Source
